Corporate Professional Support Lawyer, 5PQE+ Dubai
Corporate Professional Support Lawyer, 5PQE+ Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This top tier global law firm is looking for a mid-level PSL to join its market-leading office in Dubai.
Applicants will ideally hold a strong transactional background as an associate, or alternatively a strong track record of PSL work. Primarily based in the firm’s well-regarded corporate team, strong prior experience within this field of law is required.
Responsibilities area expected to include the maintaining of current industry knowledge, the drafting of complex documents in English and a pro-active approach to seeking solutions for internal clients and colleagues. You will be both meticulous and versitile; recognising developments which require the amendment of precedents and taking responsibility for the organisation and smooth running of internal meetings and training programmes. Furthermore, business development responsibilities will be key to the role; working alongside Partners and managing administrative aspects of client pitches as well as organising and initiating client development activities.
Those able to demonstrate the above experience and interests are invited to send their CV to Matt Yore in the JLegal UAE office located in Dubai.
